Package: hhinfection
Type: Package
Title: Models secondary infections in household clusters
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Matthew Gibson
Maintainer: Matthew Gibson <mdg583@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides functions to simulate secondary infections in
  household clusters, based on given primary infections and an underlying
  erdos-renyi graph model with a given secondary attack rate. It can also be used
  to compute probabilities (likelihoods) for final infection numbers in a
  houeshold given household sizes and primary infection numbers.
License: cran.r-project.org/web/licenses/MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
